Sesus Kiristu zotsa naro maha. Sesus Kiristu taparakta Abarão tsekokatsa niy. Idiri Dawi niwatihi taparakta Abarão tsekokatsa niy.
Ibo ka batu hyrizikwy — Byriktsa! Abykyhy mopurukze tu — niy. Iwa niy. Iwaze nipurukze Sose taskyrywy Sesus zinaroko niy.
— Berẽhe bo pãotaha: Nabo makuskyrytsa tysibanaha! Makuskyrytsa petok ziytyk tsehenahatsa, tysibabaiknaha! — niy. Hyỹ niaha. Petok ziytyk tseheze niy sisukmotsa harere humo. Nitsasonahaze nawa zuruze byrisoik izoize ana humo makuskyrytsa petok ziytyk tsehenahatsa nisiba tsihikik. Iwa hỹ.
— Taparaka mysapybyitsa tsikykaranaha. Abaka batu. Mekywa tu tsimoziknaha, mysapybara tahamoewybaiknaha — niaha. Iwa nisiharasusuze niaha.
“Bijoikpe iknyktsa Deus tsumuẽhĩtsitsa ikia bo nasiakzo.
— O kytsa ahamysapybara ty tsimoewynaha! Abaka Deus zipehata mozumu iwatsahi ityryktsa tsimoziknaha nawa zuruze botu izumu — niy.
— Ikiahatsa poro watsa tsimaha. Myzubaha mysitsumuẽhĩnaha. Katsaktsa poro mydisahawy tsimytsakykynahaze tisapyrẽna my. Iwa ikiahatsa kytsa tsimysitsumuẽhĩnahaze tisapyrẽna my. Poro mytsarakbyrize ba ziktsakykynaha. Poro wytyk kykywy humo batu sapy. Iwaze ape bo tututaha. Tahorobaik zuba. Ana bete kytsa mopaparibaiknaha. Ikiahatsa ahamysapybyitsa tu tsimykaranaha zeka ustsa kytsa batu isty tsumuẽhĩ poro iõrỹkbara wa tsimoziknaha.
“Tsimytsaso zeka ‘Uta iwa tihi my’ atsatu tsimy. Hawa ha ty Deus okze ka tsimytsasoko atsatu tsimy” — niaha.
“O asaktsa simysapyrẽtsa” mykaranaha. Deus okzeka batu. Asaktsa bijoikpe eze tu batu sihuakak. Deus sapyhaty batu sibo nyny my.
Iwaze ustsa kytsa batu sihyrinymyry ikiahatsa batu hauk tsimaha zeka ana humo batu sihyrinymyry. Deus zuba ahasoho zinymyry. Hawa ty tsimahaze kytsa papatu tsimaha zeka Deus ahabo iktsa my atahi isapyrẽnikia ty ahabo nyny my — Sesus niy.
Sesus tihi:
Kytsa nisihyrinymyryze Sesus tihi:
Iwa Isaijas Sesus soho tubabatu ziwataha, anahi Sesus nikara, iwatahi Isaijas harere wasani niy.
— O tsiksizokta! katsa mybaze ba ziktare. Tsimyparakta! — niaha. Iwaze niparak.
— Batu aty tohi duabohotsa tsik ezytyk ty ba sirara hwyk ibykta bo ba zisusu my. Iwa myzeka duabohotsa tsik ezytyk mynapytoze ibykta tsasuk mytok niy. Mopokobaik. Isuk ibykta pimyibaik iwaze duabohotsa tsik mypukuba. Duabohotsa tsik ezytyk hi tsasuk ezytyk eze tu tsipisusuku. Iwaze duabohotsa tsik isuk kino tisapyrẽna maha — Sesus niy.
— Paikpa mytsaty mykaranaha batu siaku. Hozipyrykzatsa watsa, hozipyrykzatsa siperynymyrybyitsa hỹ — mytsaty nikara.
24-25 Abaka pahahyrinymyry hawa kytsa sisopyk ikiahatsa katuktsa babatsa tsimaha zeka kawata tsipinymyryky. Aty pinymyrykyta batu puẽtsik ziky. Pinymyryziu zeka tahyrinymyrykytsa wata mozik. Estuda mopyk zeka tahyrinymyrykytsa wata mozik. Tahyrinymyrykytsa ihumo tsakurẽta. Sitsumuẽhĩtsa niwatihi. Maku sitsumuẽhĩtsa puẽtsik tatu ipehatsa ihyrizikwani. Sitsumuẽhĩtsa tapehatsa watsa mozik zeka ipehatsa ihumo tsakurẽta.
— Suão bo tsipiksizonahaktsa! Hawa ha bo iktsa tsimaha, hawa tsiwabynaha ana ty hi Suão bo typamykysonahaktsa!
— O kazo abazubata. Ikia hi bijoikpe ezektsa pehatsa. Ikia hi mybarawy ezektsa pehatsa. Ikia zuba wasani tsimykara. Tapara hawa tsimykara sihyrinymyrẽtsa bo ziokpitsĩ. Batu isty watawy. Sihyrinymyrẽtsa papatu batu isty watawy. Asaktsa sihyrinymyrybyitsa tu sibo hi tsiksiwatawyky. Hawa tsimykara tsiksiwatawy. Kytsa jabasitsa watsa tsiksiwatawyky. Asaktsa batu simyi.
— Hawa mykara kytsa bo soso byitaha — niy.
Ikiahatsa pyryhyktsa watsa tsimaha. Pyryhyktsa batu simysapy maha. Ikiahatsa kino niwatihi ahaharere batu imysapy tsimaha. “Katsaktsa mysapyrẽtsa tsimaha” mybarapetu tsimykaranaha. Iwa batu tyso tsimaha. Mysapyrẽtsa tu zeka hawa ha ty wasani zuba mytsaty tsimykaranaha. Hawa kytsa mysitsumuẽhĩnaha ana bo hi mytsaty tsimykaranaha. Atakta imysapybyita tu zeka amy ty batu sapy mytsaty mykara ana humo hi imysapybyitsa ty mykara. Hawa mytsaty tsimykaranaha ana hi tsimoziknaha.
Nisiparikikze ske sak buruk wastuhu natsukunaha asaktsa piyktsa zumukunaha nisihorozukbaiknaha.
Unata zurubanahaze isukyrytsa itsuhuk bo izumu. Kytsa papatu towahaditsa nisiparikik, tirikotsa tazahara buruk towahaditsa nisiparikik, nesepykze ziksizo.
Izo bo tysioktsotsoknaha, sinini ykarawy bo tysipaparanaha. Anaeze niakmyinahatsa tahatsaputsa ty dydydy mykaranaha. Tahakyrikinaha humo mopuziukunaha.
Erodes Suão zibeze tsihikik. Kytsa Sudeutsa humo batu zik. Kytsa Suão soho:
Yhỹ niaha. Zinymyrykynahatsa pihik koikny zitsikzanaha. Iwaze Sesus kytsa sizubarẽtsa nisipeha:
— Atuk pinymyrykynahatsa taparaktsa myzotsa sopyk humo batu yhỹ nikaranaha. Tapara tahatsyhyrype piknaha iwaze tadisahanaha. Taha ty tsyhyrype pik byizeka ba zik tahadisahanaha. Asahi taha ty tsyhyrype pikbyitsa tu ziknatahadisahakanaha iwa taparaktsa harere bo batu yhỹ ziknakaranaha. Batu sapy — niaha.
Iwaze Sesus Tiro bo niparak. Sidõ bo kino niwatihi.
Iwaze Sesus ispe niy:
Iwaze Sesus tuk zinymyrykynahatsa pe — Utakta Kiristu. Abaka ana ty hi kytsa bo soso byitaha! — niy.
— Katsaktsa asoho Kiristu Deus zipehata tsimy yhỹ tsimaha. Amy humo asaktsa Moises harere sihyrinymyrytsa tihi: “Tapara Erias myziksizo bykyze zuba Kiristu mozumu”. Amy humo Erias aharaze izumu. Siharere ty mybo tsipiwatawy — niaha.
— Aty skaraba imyhyrizikwani Deus tyryktsa tuk — niaha.
“Atakta, taoke ty, tahyrytsa ty, iwatsa mysioktyhyryk katsyhyryze piktsumuẽhĩkĩnaha kyze inamy tsizubarẽna zeka okyrysaro humo tyzihuaknaha! Iwaze okyrysaro ty kabo nyny tynaha hawa ziakse zeka piserezo” niy.
Abaka ahape:
Sesus:
Iwaze tasoho ty nitsasoko. Sesus abazubata myze wastuhu ituktsa itsyhyryze tarabaja mynakaranaha batu simyhyrizikwabyitsa maha. Ustsa ituktsa itsyhyryze tarabaja tsikaeni zuba, sihyrizikwanitsa maha. Hawa mozihikik ihuak ty sibo nyny my.
— O batu iktsa zikaha. Myhyriziktsa tysizororowykta! — niaha.
— O Deus ikia ibykyhytsa jabastsa kino niwatihi hawa abo mosakibazikiknaha nisihyrinymyry. Asahi abo mosakibazikiknaha, sinymyryrẽtsa hỹ — niy. Iwa papeu humo ziwataha.
Kyze maku iykpykbita pe “Katse duabohotsa bokta sukpesapy humo tsimykta! Abaka nabo tsimykta!” niy.
Sesus tsipa humo pioktyhyry tsihikiknaha batu zikaha kytsa sizubarẽtsa pokso. Kytsa Sesus soho — Atakta Deus sohokotsa humo ka tsimaha — niaha. Iwaze simyhyrizikwanitsa kytsa pokso Sesus batu zioktyhyryk.
— Abazubata Sesa hyrikoso okyrysaro humo — niaha. Sesus ispe niy:
Deus hi Kiristu zipehata:
Aty bijoikpe motsasoze iwaze iharere humo ja wasani, niwazuba atakta bijoikpe eze tu kino motsasoko iwaze iharere wasani my. Bijoikpe Deus dyhywy wata zubata my — Sesus niy.
Iwa sinini mykaranaha. Bykyze sinini puẽtsik maha. Hawa wytyk tsimyitsapyrẽtatsa tabykyhy pipurukze, bykyze sinini mykara puẽtsik atatsa watsa kytsa sinini mykaranaha. Bykyze puẽtsik sinini mykaranaha.
Iwaze bijoikpe eze iwatawy natakahaze utakta Deus zikpehata mynasikzo piwatawy. Kytsa aparakbaha anawatahawy bo hi iktsa maha. Ana bo iktsa mahaze sipybyrẽtsa. Mybarawy ezektsa kapokso mopuziukunaha. Utakta bijoikpe satata tuk mynasik iwa kytsa kabo iktsa maha. Mynasikze kamysapyrẽta kahyrizikporẽta kazikwyrẽta ana bo iktsa mahaze mopuziukunaha. Kamysapyrẽta tu iwatsatu mopuziukunaha.
Sityrykduwybyiza mytsyhyry waza sispirikpoza. Sityrykzowybyiza mytsyhyry waza batu sispirikpo. Iwa.
Kyze ustsa itsumuẽhĩtsa ibo zumuze: “Ikia aokyrysaro ty petok miutsa kabo nyny tsiky. Uta okyrysaro petok puẽtsik ziakse abaka okyrysaro ty napetok napetok abo nynyrezo my” niy.
Iwaze utakta abazubata tihi:
“Bykyze pikbezenaha. Awahoro eze mymyikaha bo tsimaha. Awahoro utakta zinymyrykynahatsa tuk hauk tsimaha” tsimaha — niy.
Kyze Sesus tuk zinymyrykynahatsa tuk niukurunaha. Kesemani isaziktsa koso bo zumunahaze ispe niy:
Kazo bo myzapyky zeka:
Kyze kytsa ibo niaha. Asaktsa:
— O amo skaraba batu harere ziky, batu aokani — niy.
Nabo zebykyryk. Anasapy kokota inarokota Sudeutsa harere iharekpokoso ziwatawy.
Piratus bo izumu. Sose:
Ispe niaha:
Iwaze Sesus Suão bo izumu. Nasare iknykta. Nasare Karireja eze tu. Suão bo zumuze, taharasusu tsihikik iwatahi ibo zumu. Suão buburu Sorodão inarokota eze kytsa nisiharasusuku. Anaeze hi Sesus kino ziharasu.
Simaõ wapyry ihumuẽzumu.
— O katukytsa wata “Kamysapybyita” tsimykara. “Deus harere bo batu yhỹ mykara” tsimy. Iwahatu paokzohik. Asopyksapybyita tu tsimykara paokzohik — niy.
— Iktsa tykta! Ikia tuk zinymyrykynahatsa tarabaja mykaranaha. Amo skaraba nawa mykaranaha. Okoroze mybyrywy eze katsaktsa batu tarabaja mysopyk. Ana kino tubabatu Moises harere papeu humo mybyrywy soho humo nimyhyrinymyryky — niaha.
Itukytsa isoho ziwabynahaze ibo zumunaha:
Iwaha soho humo nisihyrinymyryky:
Iwa nipamykysoko Deus tyryktsa sizubarẽtsa mozik. Taparaka batu sizuba aibani abazubatsa moziknaha. Hawa mostarada niubara iwatsa Deus tyryktsa mysiubaraka.
11-12 Pazaharezatsa sizubarẽtsa hara sukpe taba bo tahadisahakanaha.
Sesus zinymyry Deus zikwy zipo. Iwaze Sesus:
Ihumo sispirikpobyitsa tu ana humo hi paikpa mytsaty nikara.
Iwaze aidy atatsa ziksizo. Erodes pe niy:
Sibo nyny nyny nynyzo niy. Sesus ziubarawy iwatsahi kytsa sizubarẽtsa tahadisahakanaha. Sibo zibiakakzoze iwaze nitare tu. Bykyze:
Ihumo batu simypokzitsi, iwatsahi nisispihikbatakanahatsa.”
Atatsa Sudeubyitatsa tu Kereko harere nitsasoko. Siropenisia ezektatsa niy. Iwaze atatsa hi Sesus pe niy:
— Ikia tsamysapyrẽta ahumo ka mykurẽtsa — niy. Atsikara zitsaktsakze tatuktsa bo nyny niy:
Kyze Sesus Betesda ezektsa bo niukuru, zinymyrykynahatsa tuk zumunaha. Kytsa ihyrizikbyrita ibo izioktyhyryknaha.
Kyze mytsyhyrytsa wa zurunahaze Sesus hara bo jobonita bo kytsa nisioktyhyryk. Peduru Tsiaku Suão iwatsa nisioktyhyryk. Asa zuba, ustsaktsa nitarenaha. Sibaze meky watu itahyrity.
— Hyrikoso sapybara pibeze tsihikik. Hyrikoso sapybara humo pihik bo piharazukik izo bo pioktsokik. Iwa pibeze tsihikik — izo niy. — O tymytsumuẽhĩkta! Azikwykyta zeka tymytsumuẽhĩkta! Myhumo amypokzitsiakta! — niy.
“Batu tihikta! Ikiakta mytyrykbyita tsimy” — tsikaha.
Kyze wastuhu sizotsa tahahyrytsa Sesus bo nisioktykyryknaha.
— Kaharere wasani my. Wabyziutaha! Aty tawahoro perekek zeka katukta mozik, atakta Deus wasaniha humo tispirikporẽta mozik. Atahi abaka sẽ sizubarẽtsa wahoro ty nyny mykara, ana wata aty tatukytsa myserekek zeka, taziky, tatsy, taje, tazo, tahyrytsa tatsuhuk iwa myserekba zeka ustsa itukytsa Deus ibo nyny my. Sẽ itukytsa sizubarẽtsa hỹ.
— Pany! Uta kabo tyzioktyhyknaha! — niy. Kytsa ihyrizikubyita zihuahuahiknaha:
Ẽrykani umaha bo iktsa niaha. Tisarozubarẽta niy. Iwaze Sesus umaha bo nakpo zuk niyze iharabyita botu zuk niy. Ihara ziberiki. Isaro zuba. Batu iharaka. Aibani zuba tahara.
Iwaze ipe niaha:
Okyrysaro wata ty estuba ibo nyny niaha.
Sudeu ziwatahakata nitsasoziuku iwaze Sesus ipe niy:
Tsiwabykynahaze kytsa nokponi mysibanaha, kytsa bytykara eze kino niwatihi mysibanaha. Ahapybybyihu ja iwa my zeka mybarawy ipykbaratu.
— Utakta myziksizoze batu aty tohi nawa taize ja ziky ba sihyrinymyryhy. Batu aty tohi sinini ykarawy bo myze ba ihyrinymyryhy. Bijoikpe iknyktsa Deus tsumuẽhĩtsitsa kino ba sihyrinymyryhy. Uta kino Deus tse babata tu batu kahyrinymyryhy. Kazo zuba tsihyrinymyrẽta.
Wahoro jobo tsimydokoknaha, pokpedawy bo pykyhytu mydyhydyhywy bo iktsa tsimaha. Mysapy eze inakymy. Anaeze mymyikaha katsa mybo inakymynahaktsa! — niy. Yhỹ niaha.
Ustsa kytsa dyhy dyhy niahaze, Peduru, Suão, Tsiaku, ahatsahi nisioktyhyryk. Sesus mytsaty nikara:
Itsipa humo zioktyhyryknahaze mykyryburukta Sesus hapik niukuru. Atahi niwakik panu ty irikpidiwyhyta niy.
— O ata tihi kok Sesus tuk zinymyrykyta — niy. Iwa niyzoze:
Piratus:
Iharakibikia bo zoize inaharamwezo. Iwaze Sesus:
Iwaze atatsa itukytsa bo niy. Ipokzi nipuziukunaha. Atatsa hi:
Ikia atse mopurukze akurẽta tsimozik. Kytsa kino niwatihi atse humo sakurẽtsa moziknaha.
Niytahi bijoikpe iknykta hokda zuba niy. Batu ity nyzo.
Iwa Deus Sudeutsa mysitsumuẽhĩkĩ.
Deus mymyoktyhyrykta mybo myzipeha.
Abaka atakta mybo bijoikpe iknykta okoro hyritywaka katsa mybo myziharamweke.
Deus bo nisakibazikiknaha. Asa kino:
Iwatahi zipehata bipyritsa bo niwatihi izumu.
Ipyktsa ije:
— Aty petok suk zeka estuba nynyty isukbyita bo. Aty idisahawykyta zeka disahawybyita bo nynyty — nikara.
Soda ta Soana tse. Soana ta Resa tse. Resa ta Sorababeu tse. Sorobabeu ta Sarateu tse.
Ipe niyzo:
— Aty skaraba Sose tse ja — nikaranaha. Sesus ispe niy:
— Batu zik. Aba utakta ustsa hudikhudikwy ezektsa bo Deus harere humo mysispirikpo. Iwatahi ikzumu — niy. Deus soho ty mysispirikpo. Deus tyryktsa moziknaha.
— O kytsa “Sesus myhumo tsimypokzitsiukrẽta” tsimaha. Iwatahi ikiahatsa humo kakurẽta — niy. Iwaze ityryk niakbabata pe niy:
Iwaze duabohotsa tsik isuk kino tisapyrẽna maha. Bykyze atahi duabohotsa tsik ezytyk batu iakparawy. Asahi:
— Ahakurẽtsaktsa ikiahatsa batu amy tohi tsimaha.
Ahasukyrytsitsa tysipokzitsikinaha! Tysisapywykynahaktsa! Ahanamy ty nynyspyktaha! Iwaze ahanamy ja myzisizo. Ba ahanamy ziperynaha. Iwaze ahanamy baba Deus tuk tsizubarẽna. Deus hyrytsa tsimoziknaha.
— Wabytaha! Sudeutsa batu kahumo sispirikpo maha. Sodadutsa pehatsa watsa. Atahi kahumo ispirikpota babata Sudeutsa batu — niy.
Iwa Suão soho Deus harere ziwatahakanaha — niy.
— Atakta okyrysaro tsizubarẽna zisirezo. Atahi tsinamyrẽta tihi:
Ustsa Deus harere piwabykynaha. Asa hi riktsa harahareziktsa bo inatsukunahatsa watsa. Asahi wasania ty piwabynahaze sakurẽtsa. Riktsa siharatatsa zuba byitsa watsa asahi tsikaeni zuba zinymyrykynaha. Ziwabyziubyinahatsa tu Deus harere tsihokdarẽna humo iwaze imysapybyitsa tu mykaranaha iharere humo myspiriktsokdabanaha.
— O kanaro myzubaha iwatatu katsa myzubarẽtsa — niy. Iwaze hyrikoso sapybara sizubarẽtsa maku tuk ziaksenaha.
— Aty sa kasuk humo paik niy. Deus zikwy kaikze zipo — niy.
— O taparaktsa Deus sohokotsa nahyrizikponaha — nikaranaha.
Niytahi Sesus aparakbaha bo nipamykysokozo:
Aparakbaha Deus zikwy humo sipybyrẽtsa niyziknaha.
Niytahi usta niwatihi niy.
Wabytaha! Uta ikiahatsa bo kazikwy ty botu nyny iky. Ikiahatsa pyryhyk bete tsimyzonaha zeka ba zahasisi. Ikiahatsa pikzaha bete tsimyzonaha zeka ba zahahohoro — niy. — Batu amy tohi ahamyiwyky. Ahasukyrytsitsa humo ba zahamyiwynaha — niy.
— Yhỹ niy. Ikia tsiksikta. Bipyri wata tsimykara. Samarija ezekta wata tsimykara — niy.
— Iwaze atakta atukta humo batu kyik. Iwata tu kyik my. Pikykniki naha humo kyik my. Ata bo atsikara ty nyny my — niy. Iwa Sesus isukmota soho humo nisihyrinymyryky.
Kytsa sizubarẽtsa harape bo inakypykyknahaze Sesus ispe niy:
Iwatsahi tsipiwatawykynaha hawa taparaktsa nikaranaha ikiahatsa yhỹ tsimykaranaha. Ana kino tsipiwatawykynaha Deus tsihyrinymyrẽta.
Iwatahi tsinamyrẽta tatuk tuka mytsaty nikara:
Sispihikrẽtsa nikaranaha tozeka ja ispehakatsa unopokte ja mozumu. Tozeka ja iwariknakyrize ja mozumu Sitsumuẽhĩtsa piperykynaha zeka sakurẽtsa mykaranaha — Sesus niy.
Zopok nabybykykze. Ikiahatsa:
Uta hi wasani my mybyrykywy eze atatsa izororowy. Atatsa Abarão tsekoka. Tubabatu Satanas ziporokmyitatsa iwatatsahi ba buruhuwa ziktoziky niy — Sesus nikara.
Wabytaha! Uta piksi maku tawahoro perikik tawata. Kytsa wahoro inakarabaik. Deus tihi hudikhudikwy soho nakarakbaik niy. Uta ape my ikiahaka ba ziknyzonaha. Ikiahatsa tsimytsasokonaha zeka, “Atakta Deus zipehata myziksizo tsimaha ihumo mykurẽtsa tsimoziknaha, iharere bo hyỹ tsimaha. Iwaze ihumo mykurẽtsa tsimoziknaha” iwaze tsipiknyzonaha — niy.
“Aidykta! Nanabyitaba sihudikhudikwy taba! Ske buruk tykuru! Sinamybyikitsa siekbyritsa sihyrizikubyitsa pãozikahabyitsa iwahatsa tynasioktyhyryknaha” niy! Hyỹ niy.
— Estuba wytyk mytsozikewy tsizubarẽna niy. Mytsozikewy mytsyhyrytsa waha parata hi. Estuba pihokda zeka iwatatsahi mytsozikewy piberi.
“Batu. O atuk mynapykyryk ta tu. Tsimyzikpehakaze uta hyỹ mynakara. Iwatatu batu katy myikaha. Batu pikuza ty tybeze. Atse anamy ziaksebaikta tu iwaze wytykyryk humo ziwebaik, iwaze anamy zipykta tu sa ziksizoze tumy tsipikuku itsyhyryze pikuza tsibeze” niy.
Niytahi Sesus Pariseutsa bo nipamykysokoze ispe niy:
Sesus:
— Deus tyryktsa bo ka ba zikozonaha. Kytsa iwatawy piberikinaha zeka ba zikozonaha niy.
Abaka haramukuka pikykniki. Iwatahi haramukuka pitsumuẽhĩ. Atatsa tasukyrytsa harere soho piwaby. Uta hi atatsa pibetesaka. Iharere ty waby byizeka pikyknizo. Kakubyri mozumu zeka kakidipyk mynaparak” niy — Sesus nikara.
— Ikia aba estubaha tsimy. Anamy ty sinamybyitsa bo nyny tsimy. Aokyrysaro humo kino niwatihi nynybaik tsimy. Iwaze hi anamy baba Deus sapy eze tu my. Anamy baba ty mynapykyk. Bykyze pany! Kapik tynao — niy.
Iwaze izumuze Sesus tihi:
Iwatatu maku myhyrizikwani ispehatsa niyzik. Iwaze tahudikhudikwy ziksizoze tatsumuẽhĩtsitsa bo nisihuahua. Iwaze sitsumuẽhĩtsitsa ibo zumunaha ispe niy:
Zisatsuknahaze zihitsa ispe niy:
Taparaktsa asa zuba nipamykysokonaha.
Asaktsa simysapybyitsa tu mykaranaha ana humo hi Sesus tsihyrinymyrẽta.
tysipykwy apokso sipybyrẽtsa’.”
